From one of the most recognised and reputed fashion brands
column13: Guess
column14:
comes this ultra-fashionably designed women\u2019s personal timekeeper from its Little Party Girl series of classic analog watches.

\r\n

\r\n\tAs with most of the watches that come under this series
column15: this Guess analog watch too flaunts a lot of specialized aesthetic elements that include high-quality metallic finish
column16:
a gorgeous leather strap and a generous measure of crystals or semi-precious stones.

\r\n

\r\n\tThe timekeeping function on this extremely elegant watch works on the popular quartz crystal technology
column17: which uses small bar shaped crystals of quartz. These quartz crystals work by generating an electrical charge which causes them to vibrate at a thousand times a second
column18:
making them extremely stable resonators for extremely accurate timekeeping.

Body & Design

This artistically crafted watch sports a round dial that measures 36 mm in diameter with a 7 mm thickness
column19:
while also sporting an extensive amount of crystal stone work on and around the dial. The watch face has absolutely no hour markers but features a significant amount of crystal stones that are placed on a neat and light coloured background.

\r\n

\r\n\tThis highly aesthetic dial has a considerable circle of protection in the form of a sturdy and durable stainless steel case. The stainless steel bezel which forms the upper portion of the case is studded with a brilliant crystal stone set making the watch a sure eye-catcher.The time indicating hands on the dial also have the same metallic colour as the dial\u2019s case. This well-planned colour combination within the dial lets you easily differentiate between the various elements on the dial
column20:
leading to effortless and hassle-free time reading. The watch’s round dial with its glamorous stone set arrangement is kept safely and securely attached to your wrist at ball times with the help of its sensual and exceedingly stylish leather strap. This strap can be easily fastened and unfastened by using its stylish and effective buckle clasp.

Functions and Other Features

The time displayed on the dial can be easily adjusted or changed with the watch’s rotating crown which is placed on the right of the dial’s case. The dial along with all its delicate and minute internal working parts are kept in working condition with a durable mineral crystal glass cover. This combination of the stainless steel case and the mineral crystal glass gives the dial the ability to be water-resistant up to a maximum depth of 10 m. With such sophistication and elegance
column21:
this absolute stunner of a wristwatch from the Guess Little Party Girl series is sure to find its way and be part of your prized watch collection.

\n

column15: which uses small bar shaped crystals of quartz or silicon dioxide. These quartz crystals work by generating an electrical charge which causes them to vibrate at a thousand times a second
column16:

Sporting an elegant round dial with a 40 mm diameter with a 10 mm case depth
column17: this highly fashionable analog timepiece from Guess flaunts a light coloured watch face with a beautiful mother of pearl finish. The digit markers on the dial are in the form of small rectangular bars with the exception of the 12
column19: 6 and 9 o\u2019clock positions
column20:
which are featured as Roman numerals.

The watch’s three time-indicating hands are also given a rich metallic finish which is exactly the same as on the digit markers. This very thoughtful colour combination used on the dial makes it very easy to gauge the time with just a single glance at the dial. The dial is surrounded by a sturdy stainless steel case which provides the dial with sizeable protection against low intensity impacts and shock.

The time displayed on the watch face can easily be adjusted or changed by using the watch’s rotating crown which is located on the right side of the dial’s stainless steel case. The entire dial and case configuration on this watch is held firmly on your wrist with a very impressive leather strap.
